<div class="comm-page">

  <div class="comm-page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="comm-page-tag">Commissions</span>
      <h1 class="comm-page-heading">We're currently<br>closed for<br>commissions.</h1>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="comm-page-body">

      <p class="comm-page-intro">We open commissions in small batches to make sure every custom piece gets the care it deserves. Right now our slots are full — but we're not gone.</p>

      <div class="comm-page-box">
        <p class="comm-page-box-label">Have something special in mind?</p>
        <p class="comm-page-box-copy">If you have a unique request or a character that means a lot to you, drop us a message. We review every email and will do our best to accommodate truly special projects.</p>
        <a class="comm-page-email-btn" href="/pages/contact">Get in touch &rarr;</a>
      </div>

      <div class="comm-page-details">
        <div class="comm-page-detail">
          <span class="comm-page-detail-label">When we reopen</span>
          <span class="comm-page-detail-value">Spots are announced via our store — check back soon.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="comm-page-detail">
          <span class="comm-page-detail-label">What we make</span>
          <span class="comm-page-detail-value">Anime, games, movies, TV — any character, any size.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="comm-page-detail">
          <span class="comm-page-detail-label">Turnaround</span>
          <span class="comm-page-detail-value">Typically 3–6 weeks from deposit to delivery.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

</div>

